snippet.title: Crowd Stops in Awe as 4-Year-Old Sings ‘Goodness of God’
snippet.description:
When Karolina Protsenko introduced her 4-year-old brother Nicholas to the crowd, no one expected what happened next. Nicholas sat at the piano and began to sing Goodness of God with such pure emotion that the crowd stopped in awe.
Some started singing along, others just stood still — many said they had never experienced anything like it. 🎹 Goodness of God cover by 4-year-old Nicholas Protsenko and his sister Karolina is a truly beautiful moment of sibling harmony, worship, and talent.

✨ Watch as this street performance melts hearts and inspires everyone who hears it.

snippet.title: Phaphey Kuttniyan (Movie Trailer) | Neeru Bajwa | Tania | Gurbaaz Singh | New Punjabi Movie 2025
snippet.description:
The trailer of ‘Phaphey Kuttniyan’, offers a sneak peek into what promises to be one of the most entertaining Punjabi movies of 2025. Starring powerhouse performers Neeru Bajwa and Tania, the film blends humour, emotion, and drama rooted in the colourful chaos.

Directed with a refreshing take on comedy, Phaphey Kuttniyan is set to deliver laughs and life lessons in equal measure. The chemistry between the lead actresses, paired with a vibrant supporting cast, makes this trailer a must-watch for fans of Punjabi cinema. If you love films that balance tradition, emotion, and clever comedy, this one’s for your 2025 watchlist.
